<span id="freeTextContainer16862737662112781283">Happiness Power: How to Unleash Your Power and Lead a More Joyful Life is a wonderful guide to enjoying your life. Use it to help boost your overall happiness or pick certain steps to work on when needed as a reminder. Robert Gill Jr. combines his professional experience with the latest research. He also backs up these claims with quotes from some of my favorite &apos;happiness experts&apos; in the industry, like Gretchen Rubin and Arianna Huffington. <br/><br/>Perhaps the best part about this book is the checklist</span>
  <span id="freeText16862737662112781283" style="display:none">Happiness Power: How to Unleash Your Power and Lead a More Joyful Life is a wonderful guide to enjoying your life. Use it to help boost your overall happiness or pick certain steps to work on when needed as a reminder. Robert Gill Jr. combines his professional experience with the latest research. He also backs up these claims with quotes from some of my favorite 'happiness experts' in the industry, like Gretchen Rubin and Arianna Huffington. <br /><br />Perhaps the best part about this book is the checklists you can download in the front of the book. It truly is a happiness guide you can follow step-by-step for years to come. The strategies are actionable. Some are quick, while others take more time to develop. But whatever tips readers choose to follow, there is value in every page of this read. Highly informative and highly recommended for everyone. </span>
