<div id="review_3894586584" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3894586584" />
    <a title="Jodi Davis" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7667621-jodi-davis"><img alt="Jodi Davis" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1510783456p2/7667621.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3894586584?book_show_action=true">Mar 17, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jodi Davis" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jodi Davis" href="/user/show/7667621-jodi-davis">Jodi Davis</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer3894586584&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3894586584" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15858487978189395592">Don’t worry... be happy! This amazing book is all about happiness- it covers the who, what, when, where, why, and most importantly, HOW! I loved that the author pointed out that happiness is not about what we have, but how we feel about what we have, and goes into how physical, mental, spiritual, and relational influences of happiness. And, even better, he backs it up with research studies (that doesn’t read like research!) - a really good read, highly recommend- 5/5 stars</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

