 cool. But they have deadly side effects. One person went crazy and another died. And anyone who seeks treatment risks being identified by the Faction. But that secret government agency isn’t the only one looking for us. An evil Altered named Silas is using mind control on other Altereds, trying to bring on an apocalypse, and he’s close to doing it! Me and my friends are trying to stop him and hide from the Faction. But Silas isn’t a pushover. He kidnapped my family and is using his mind-controlled freaks to catch us. In order to save my family, I’ll have to risk my life and outsmart a madman who wants to make me his sock puppet. And if I fail, everyone I love will die. <\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"8955912937205690395\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'12_book_56763337\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"KRkHJV5b/o8NGpAoQt9j9SkAro+l2dyRmvHpHMfTWgoEtDHHkhnq1ia/qYOj3CZVZdDdO1I+47jRoFJ9gGP2gg==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"56763337\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"12_book_56763337\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\